Dependency Information

Apache Maven

<dependency>
  <groupId>at.rseiler.pom-project</groupId>
  <artifactId>pom</artifactId>
  <version>1.1</version>
  <type>pom</type>
</dependency>

Apache Buildr

'at.rseiler.pom-project:pom:pom:1.1'

Apache Ant

<dependency org="at.rseiler.pom-project" name="pom" rev="1.1">
  <artifact name="pom" type="pom" />
</dependency>

Groovy Grape

@Grapes(
@Grab(group='at.rseiler.pom-project', module='pom', version='1.1')
)

Grails

compile 'at.rseiler.pom-project:pom:1.1'

Leiningen

[at.rseiler.pom-project/pom "1.1"]

SBT

libraryDependencies += "at.rseiler.pom-project" %% "pom" % "1.1"
